name: Maze Walker - Medical Supplies
description: You are on your way to deliver medical supplies to the hospital when your truck breaks down. You forgot your cell phone so you can't call anyone for help. The quickest way to the hospital is through the open field maze run by the Open Field Mob! They are ruthless and known to use exotic guard animals in place of guard dogs. Unfortunately, this is the only option you have if you're going to make it to the hospital on time to make your delivery . Good luck!
